sentences: Jo Dong-rim (Korean: 조동림; born March 25, 1985), better known by the stage name Mad Clown (Korean: 매드클라운), is a South Korean rapper, songwriter, and record producer.
He debuted with the single "Luv Sickness" in 2008 and released his first extended play, Anything Goes, in 2011.
